title: KCET CUTOFF 2022
content:
What was the KCET cutoff for CSE RR campus in 2022?
(General merit)
(Round wise cutoffs will be helpful)
Thanks in advance!!

comments.body: You can search it up on the official KEA website, they have a seat matrix with round-wise cutoffs for all the different courses. PES CSE at RR campus cut off at rank 787 iirc in the first round.
It was <1000 for first two rounds.

The PDF isn't loading,some issue
So asked here
Anyways,thank you

Ohh
Any idea about the third round?
Thank u!!
